OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with the odd
OL,6,Fspot of light rain. Bright spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping through the morning then
OL,8,Ffurther rain is likely for a time in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will clear northeast
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, turning heavy for
OL,13,Fa time. Then staying dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith variable cloud and clear spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,17,Fthis soon breaking up through the
OL,18,Fmorning. Staying dry and warm with
OL,19,Fprolonged bright or sunny spells
OL,20,Fthrough the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
