OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudier
OL,6,Fin the northwest with some patchy
OL,7,Flight rain on Sunday. Otherwise
OL,8,Fstaying warm and dry with plenty of
OL,9,Fbright or sunny weather from Sunday to
OL,10,FTuesday.
